<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<FindBugsFilter xmlns="https://github.com/spotbugs/filter/3.0.0">
  <!--
    Reviewed suppressions (Chapter 16: suppress with a reason, never disable a whole detector).

    This module has NONE: that is the chapter's point made by the build. The domain types are
    immutable records and value classes, and the one type that stores a collection copies it in and
    copies it out (Item 50), so the representation-exposure detectors (EI_EXPOSE_REP / EI_EXPOSE_REP2)
    stay quiet without any suppression. The filter is kept (empty) so a future, genuinely-reviewed
    suppression has a home with a reason, rather than being added inline.
  -->
</FindBugsFilter>
